<aside class="notice">
  A unique <code>email</code> is required
</aside>

Create a user. An email invitation will be sent to the specified email if role is not "no-access".
The user will be able to create a password using the link in the invitation email.

Use the <code>merge</code> attribute to merge the candidate attributes in case a candidate with a matching email address already exists.
